Print["PART 12: Adjoint action and left-right connection"];
Print["================================================================"];

(* The 6x6 adjoint of (R, T):
   Ad(f) = [[R, 0], [[T]_x R, R]]
   
   Left-right covariance connection:
   Sigma_l^{-1} = J_lr^T Sigma_r^{-1} J_lr
   where J_lr = Ad(f_0) = [[R_0, 0], [[T_0]_x R_0, R_0]]
*)

